<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Yah Ventures | Coming Soon</title>

<style>
*{
margin:0;
padding:0;
box-sizing:border-box;
font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;
}

body{
background:#0b0b0b;
color:white;
display:flex;
justify-content:center;
align-items:center;
height:100vh;
text-align:center;
padding:20px;
}

.container{
max-width:850px;
}

img{
width:220px;
margin-bottom:30px;
}

h1{
font-size:58px;
letter-spacing:8px;
margin-bottom:10px;
}

.gold{
color:#D4AF37;
}

.green{
color:#00B36B;
}

.tagline{
font-size:22px;
margin-bottom:30px;
letter-spacing:2px;
}

.description{
font-size:20px;
color:#d5d5d5;
line-height:1.8;
margin-bottom:45px;
}

.button{
display:inline-block;
padding:16px 38px;
border:2px solid #D4AF37;
color:white;
text-decoration:none;
border-radius:50px;
font-size:18px;
transition:.3s;
}

.button:hover{
background:#D4AF37;
color:black;
}

.footer{
margin-top:60px;
color:#999;
font-size:16px;
}
</style>

</head>

<body>

<div class="container">

<img src="logo.png" alt="Yah Ventures">

<h1>
<span class="gold">YAH</span>
VENTURES
</h1>

<div class="tagline">
ONE VISION. MANY VENTURES.
</div>

<div class="description">
Building businesses that create opportunities,
innovation and lasting impact.
</div>

<a class="button" href="#">
COMING SOON
</a>

<div class="footer">
© 2026 Yah Ventures. All Rights Reserved.
</div>

</div>

</body>
</html>
